<p>Is there a way to pass a text file with failed cucumber features to parallel_cucumber? </p>  <p><br> <strong>Example:</strong> You have a cucumber.yml with a parallel profile</p>  <pre><code>#cucumber.yml parallel: -r features --format ParallelTests::Cucumber::FailuresLogger --out rerun.txt </code></pre>  <p>you can run </p>  <p><code>bundle exec parallel_cucumber -o "-p parallel" </code></p>  <p>You can run the output <code>rerun.txt</code> file with the command</p>  <p><code>bundle exec cucumber @rerun.txt</code></p>  <p>How can I rerun the failures in parallel?</p>